data.description: 820 Brierly Lane in West Mifflin is located in a very convenient location close to the WM school campus and The Waterfront in Homestead.  This brick 2 story home has an inviting front & side covered porch for enjoying the great seasons in Pittsburgh.  The living and dining rooms have hardwood flooring.  The kitchen has been extended to the back addition which meets the the large family room with a wood burning fireplace.  The kitchen has a ton of cabinets and counter space and will accommodate a large gathering.  There is a deck overlooking the back yard and is accessed from the family room.  The powder room is off of the family room.  Upstairs are 2 bedrooms with hardwood flooring and a full bath.  The lower level has a finished basement, storage, a full bath, and a 2 car integral garage.  Inground pool in the back yard.
